cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is about person re-identification, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses deep learning and model training, which suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves unsupervised learning, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with multimedia data, which could place it under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper discusses the limitations of clustering methods, which could place it under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
